text: WETL (91.7 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of South Bend, Indiana. The station is owned by the South Bend Community School Corporation, and airs an educational format. The station was assigned the WETL call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on March 19, 1959. ==References== ==External links== * ETL Category:Radio stations established in 1959 Category:1959 establishments in Indiana Category:High school radio stations in the United States Category:St. Joseph County, Indiana
